<html>
  <body>
    <p>
      Someone just requested to change your {{ realmName }} account's
      credentials. If this was you, click on the link below to reset them.
    </p>
    <p><a href="{{ link }}">Link to reset credentials</a></p>
    <p>
      This link will expire within {{#linkExpirationFormatter
      }}{{ linkExpiration }}{{/linkExpirationFormatter}}.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you don't want to reset your credentials, just ignore this message and
      nothing will be changed.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>